70010000080279.description:
An abandoned house, a locked room, somewhere in the distance you hear the steps of your kidnapper... How to escape? You'll have to secretly explore the house, find hidden objects and use them to escape from the maniac!

Be extremely careful and act quietly so as not to attract the attention of a maniac. Your footsteps, the creaking of doors or the noise of an accidentally dropped mug can attract the attention of your kidnapper. Sneak like a shadow, collect various tools to open locked boxes and hiding places and find your way to the exit!

You have several attempts, so try not to get caught by the maniac. Can you find the path to freedom?

GAME FEATURES:
• The heart-stopping genre of escape from a maniac;
• Detailed levels with puzzles;
• Fun and addictive escape gameplay;
• Intense and atmospheric soundtrack.

70010000081771.description:
Is it just me, or are those... pawprints all over the streets of Rome? And where there’s pawprints, there’s cats! Let's search for them!

Hidden Cats in Rome is a short and pleasant hidden objects game for everyone – look around a big, lovely illustration, relax, and spot all the furry friends hiding in every nook and cranny. Starting with a beautiful (yet monochromatic) scenery, the city fills itself with warm colours the more cats you find!

Features:
- Gorgeous hand-drawn sceneries to look around;
- Two main game modes, one more challenging than the other;
- Extra unlockable stages with little kittens!;
- Relaxing music and ambient;
- Over 900 cats… and other things to find :)

70010000071126.description:
READY! STEADY! GO!

A real racer can handle both a real car and a radio-controlled toy car. Win races, complete the championship and come to the finish line first!

The game offers colourful and vibrant cartoon graphics that immerse players in the exciting world of toy car racing. A huge number of jumps, stunts, amazing turns and unimaginable battles for victory await you.

What makes the game especially fun is the local multiplayer mode, where two or even four participants can compete with each other in exciting races. Both co-op and competitive modes will be available, allowing players to enjoy competition and big jumps and stunts together with friends.

Get your toy cars ready, turn on the turbo and get ready for mind-blowing races along dangerous tracks!

GAME FEATURES:
• Various types of racing cars;
• Local multiplayer for 2 and 4 players;
• Many racing tracks of varying difficulty;
• Nice physics of radio-controlled cars;
• Colourful cartoon graphics.
